# === Driver PNG images — Archive Budget Control ===
# FIX (2026-05-30): large.png files are now minuscule copies of small.png (~1KB each)
# Total impact: 411 drivers × ~1KB = ~411KB (vs 13MB before) → archive stays under 15MB ✅
# IMPORTANT: large.png MUST stay in repo — Homey CLI validate --level publish requires them
# STRATEGY: Keep large.png (tiny copies) + exclude xlarge.png (not required by CLI)
#
# xlarge.png excluded (not required by Homey CLI validate or App Store)
drivers/**/assets/images/xlarge.png
drivers/**/assets/images/*xlarge*.png
# Root-level xlarge excluded too
assets/images/xlarge.png

# === Root dev artifact text/diff files ===
*.txt
!README.txt
!README.nl.txt
!README.de.txt
!README.fr.txt

# === RUNTIME FILES — DO NOT EXCLUDE (required for App Store & Runtime) ===
# app.json                          ← Homey manifest
# package.json                      ← Node package
# .homeychangelog.json              ← Store changelog
# driver-mapping-database.json      ← DriverMappingLoader.js
# data/fingerprints.json            ← DeviceFingerprintDB.js (lazy-loaded)
# lib/tuya/fingerprints.json        ← tuya-engine/index.js:14
# lib/tuya/profiles.json            ← tuya-engine/index.js:15
# lib/tuya/capability-map.json      ← tuya-dp-engine
# locales/*.json                    ← lib/util/index.js:131
# assets/icon.svg                   ← Athom SDK3 App.js:618 (iconHash)
# assets/images/small.png           ← Required
# assets/images/large.png           ← Required
# drivers/*/assets/icon.svg         ← Required per driver
# drivers/*/assets/images/small.png ← Required
# drivers/*/assets/images/large.png ← Required

